snippet.title: Expeditions: Conquistador gameplay with developer Logic Artists
snippet.description:
UPDATE: Here's the official video review - http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=U4WE65bM8xs

Andrew and Cassidee play Expeditions: Conquistador just days before the worldwide launch! Logic Artists were on set to give us insight and to answer all questions! --
